<% content_for :title, "The Kluster - About Baldrick" %>

<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
  <!-- Breadcrumb -->
  <%= render 'shared/breadcrumbs', breadcrumbs: [
    { title: 'Home', path: '/' },
    { title: 'Baldrick Breakthroughs', path: '/breakthroughs' },
    { title: 'The Kluster', path: nil }
  ] %>

  <!-- Main Content Card -->
  <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <%= render 'shared/page_header', title: 'The Kluster', subtitle: 'Our development and testing facility' %>

    <!-- Content Section -->
    <div class="px-8 py-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose max-w-none">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">The Kluster</h2>

          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
            The Kluster is our state-of-the-art development and testing facility where we design, prototype, and validate all Baldrick products before they reach our customers.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-400 p-4 mb-8">
            <div class="flex">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-green-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-3">
                <p class="text-sm text-green-700">
                  <strong>Quality Assurance:</strong> Every Baldrick product undergoes rigorous testing in The Kluster before release.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">What is The Kluster?</h3>

          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            The Kluster is more than just a workshop - it's our innovation hub where ideas become reality. Named for its cluster of development stations and testing equipment, this facility houses everything we need to bring Baldrick products from concept to production.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Facility Features</h3>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Development Lab</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                <li>• PCB design and prototyping</li>
                <li>• 3D printing and CNC machining</li>
                <li>• Component testing and validation</li>
                <li>• Firmware development stations</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Testing Environment</h4>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                <li>• Environmental stress testing</li>
                <li>• Performance benchmarking</li>
                <li>• Long-term reliability testing</li>
                <li>• Real-world simulation setups</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Development Process</h3>

          <div class="space-y-6 mb-8">
            <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">1. Concept & Design</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Every product starts with a concept. We brainstorm, sketch, and design solutions to real problems faced by lighting enthusiasts.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">2. Prototyping</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                We build multiple prototypes, testing different approaches and refining the design based on real-world feedback.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">3. Testing & Validation</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Every prototype undergoes extensive testing in various conditions to ensure reliability and performance.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">4. Production Preparation</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                Once validated, we prepare for production, ensuring quality control and consistency across all units.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Equipment & Capabilities</h3>

          <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-4 mb-6">
            <div class="flex">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-blue-400" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-3">
                <p class="text-sm text-blue-700">
                  <strong>State-of-the-Art Equipment:</strong> The Kluster is equipped with the latest tools and technology for product development.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4 mb-3">
                <svg class="h-12 w-12 mx-auto text-gray-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H4a1 1 0 01-1-1V4zM3 10a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H4a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6zM14 9a1 1 0 00-1 1v6a1 1 0 001 1h2a1 1 0 001-1v-6a1 1 0 00-1-1h-2z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">PCB Design</h5>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Professional PCB design and prototyping</p>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4 mb-3">
                <svg class="h-12 w-12 mx-auto text-gray-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">3D Printing</h5>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Rapid prototyping and enclosure design</p>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-4 mb-3">
                <svg class="h-12 w-12 mx-auto text-gray-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M11.3 1.046A1 1 0 0112 2v5h4a1 1 0 01.82 1.573l-7 10A1 1 0 018 18v-5H4a1 1 0 01-.82-1.573l7-10a1 1 0 011.12-.38z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h5 class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Testing</h5>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Comprehensive testing and validation</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Quality Standards</h3>

          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            Every product that comes out of The Kluster meets our high standards for quality, reliability, and performance. We test in real-world conditions, ensuring that our products work reliably in the environments where they'll be used.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-8 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 border border-gray-200">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Visit The Kluster</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              While The Kluster is primarily our development facility, we occasionally host open days and workshops for the community. Keep an eye on our events calendar for opportunities to see where the magic happens.
            </p>
            <a href="/events" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
              View Upcoming Events
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
